{
  "stem": "3874.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And of course, the counsellors recognized this, and asked the children to do this, so that's what we all did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "That's when we started.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Anyway, the war started.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And that's when we started learning about air raids, about shelters, about sandbagging, filling sandbags, and putting them in front of windows, and taping windows.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We were organized again, as far as the air raids are concerned.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "When the air raids occurred, the older children would take-- would be responsible-- there was always-- would be responsible for the younger children, and the younger children were responsible for the still younger children.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So that you always had some sort of a buddy system, that you made sure that nobody would stay in the room when the air raids occurred.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went into-- well, this particular home had a basement that was built like a fortress, with-- with curved arches, that-- I mean, it was really quite a basement.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's where we went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not only did we, the children from the home, go, but it was also an air raid shelter for some of the surrounding population, who also lived in the area.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there were not only us, but there were other people coming out to shelter whenever air raids occurred.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew the war was on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, there was news all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even though school continued, even though we still played football, you know, there were always-- the rumors started coming.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somebody saw paratroopers coming down, you know, there were talks about the fifth column with German spies coming in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I mean, there were all kinds of rumors floating around.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we read newspapers, we, by that time, we had picked up enough French to be able to read newspapers.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
